#| msgid ""
#| "&konquest; is the &kde; version of Gnu-Lactic. Players conquer other "
#| "planets by sending ships to them. The goal is to build an interstellar "
#| "empire and ultimately conqueror all other player's planets. &konquest; "
#| "can be played against other people or a computer."
msgid ""
"&konquest; is the &kde; version of &gnu-lactic;. Players conquer other "
"planets by sending ships to them. The goal is to build an interstellar "
"empire and ultimately conqueror all other player's planets. &konquest; can "
"be played against other people or a computer."
msgstr ""
"&konquest; é a versión para &kde; de Gnu-Lactic. Os xogadores conquistan "
"outros planetas enviando naves. O obxectivo é construír un imperio "
"interestelar e finalmente conquistar todos os planetas dos demais xogadores. "
"&konquest; pódese xogar contra outras persoas ou contra un computador."

