#, no-c-format
msgid "Ships cannot be stopped once they leave a planet."
msgstr "As naves non poden deterse unha vez que deixan o planeta."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:220
#, no-c-format
msgid "Ships cannot attack other ships in midair."
msgstr "As naves non poden atacar outras naves no medio do espazo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:221
#, no-c-format
msgid "Ships can be stored at planets for later use."
msgstr "As naves pódense almacenar nos planetas para usalas máis tarde."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:222
#, no-c-format
msgid "A planet cannot be given away."
msgstr "Non é posíbel entregar un planeta."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:223
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A player can skip a turn by pressing <guibutton>End Turn</guibutton> without "
"launching any ships."
msgstr ""
"Un xogador pode saltar a súa rolda premendo <guibutton>Rematar a rolda</"
"guibutton> sen botar ningunha nave."

#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:228
#, no-c-format
msgid "Strategies and Tips"
msgstr "Estratexias e suxestións"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:231
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The game is all about ship production. Try to get as many planets as "
"possible as fast as you can in order to build more ships than any of your "
"opponents."
msgstr ""

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:232
#, fuzzy, no-c-format
#| msgid "Do not attack a planet with less than 10 ships."
msgid ""
"Do not attack a planet with less than 10 ships, unless you can conquer it."
msgstr "Non ataques un planeta con menos de dez naves."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:233
#, no-c-format
msgid "Attack neutral planets before other players' planets."
msgstr "Ataca os planetas neutrais antes dos planetas dos demais xogadores."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:234
#, no-c-format
msgid "Split your ship storages across several planets."
msgstr "Divide as túas reservas de naves entre varios planetas."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:235
#, no-c-format
msgid "Plan your attacks in advance."
msgstr "Planea os ataques con antelación."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:236
#, no-c-format
msgid "Use the ruler to find out the distance between planets."
msgstr "Usa a regra para saber a distancia entre planetas."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:237
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use the information window to get information on planets before an attack."
msgstr ""
"Usa a xanela de información para obter información sobre os planetas antes "
"dun ataque."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:238
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If this information is available to you, it is preferable to attack a planet "
"with a low kill ratio from a planet with a high one."
msgstr ""
"Se esta información está dispoñíbel, é preferíbel atacar un planeta cunha "
"porcentaxe de mortes baixa a un planeta cunha porcentaxe alta."

