#. Tag: title
#: index.docbook:336
#, no-c-format
msgid "Frequently Asked Questions"
msgstr "Preguntas frecuentes"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:340
#, no-c-format
msgid "Can I redirect ships once they have left a planet?"
msgstr "Podo redirixir as naves unha vez que saian dun planeta?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:341
#, no-c-format
msgid "No, once ships leave a planet, they cannot be stopped or redirected."
msgstr ""
"Non, unha vez que as naves saen dun planeta non se poden deter ou redirixir."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:345
#, no-c-format
msgid "Do the different colors and shapes of planets mean anything?"
msgstr "Significan algo as cores e formas dos planetas?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:346
#, no-c-format
msgid "No, they are random."
msgstr "Non, son ao chou."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:350
#, no-c-format
msgid "How can I know where my ships are?"
msgstr "Como sei onde están as miñas naves?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:351
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Click <guibutton>Show Standings</guibutton>. It will give you information "
"about fleets currently in flight."
msgstr ""
"Preme <guibutton>Amosar a situación</guibutton>. Dá información sobre as "
"frotas que están en voo."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:355
#, no-c-format
msgid "I have lost all my planets, but I am still in the game, why?"
msgstr "Perdín todos os meus planetas pero aínda estou no xogo. Por que?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:356
#, no-c-format
msgid "You have not lost the game until you have lost all your ships."
msgstr "Non se perde a partida ata ter perdidas todas as naves."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:360
#, no-c-format
msgid "Can I store ships on a planet for later use?"
msgstr "Podo almacenar naves nun planeta para usalas máis tarde?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:361
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Yes, you should however store them on multiple planets to be able to send "
"them to nearby planets."
msgstr ""
"Si. Porén, deberíalas almacenar en varios planetas para podelas enviar a "
"planetas próximos."

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:365
#, no-c-format
msgid "Is it possible to change the theme?"
msgstr "É posíbel cambiar o tema?"

#. Tag: para
#: index.docbook:366
#, no-c-format
msgid "No, that is not possible at the moment."
msgstr "Non, de momento non é posíbel."

